description:
It’s been a year of awakening for so many (myself included). I woke up about A LOT of things. 

You know when you’re a young child you don’t pay any mind to the world around you besides your own little one? You believe the people in #government roles are there because they are worthy.. trusting.. honest..care about you and your life. 

Then, you grow up and realize many of them aren’t what you once thought. All the hypocrisy and utter craziness becomes all too obvious... as if someone took a blindfold off. 

The truth is spewing out like a busted pipe. At first, a leak.. and now the pressure is building. The hole is getting bigger.. soon it’s going to burst. 

I’ve created a TRUTH Series covering topics I’ve been digging into lately. I decided to share because it’s important and today was validation of so many things. 

Today I’m sharing a first hand account from someone on the frontlines. A TRUE hero, patient advocate, and RN. A truth seeker like me. Names and locations aren’t mentioned for obvious reasons. 

Unfortunately, this story is validation of what I’ve believed to be happening everywhere throughout this entire “pandemic”. Unethical business and big money.. It’s all in my stories... 

#covid19 #scamdemic #mask #bigpharma #truthseeker #truth #liberty #freedom #leadright #raisedright #kag #maga #trump2020 #pandemic #cdc #america #unitedwestand #prayerwarrior #conservativewomen #womenfortrump
